reviewText: I originally got to see these cartoons on Australia's SBS channel, and found them very funny, in a bad-taste kind of way. Revisiting this material, some of it is very clever and some is the reverse. If you're prepared to be forgiving towards those less than inspired moments, this brand of left-wing comedy could be just your cup of non-fair-trade coffee. I was glad that this DVD arrived promptly and in good condition.
